      <item>
        <title>How to integrate google tag manager analytics</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mmczaplinski]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hey <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/dejangeorgiev">@dejangeorgiev</a></p>
<p>The name of the property should be <code>googleTagManagerAnalytics</code> <img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=9" title=":slight_smile:" class="emoji" alt=":slight_smile:"></p>
<p>So, your code should be:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-javascript">{
    name: "@frontity/google-tag-manager-analytics",
    state: {
        googleTagManagerAnalytics: {
            containerId: 'GTM-NBGPD9N'
        },
    },
},
</code></pre>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/how-to-integrate-google-tag-manager-analytics/2451/2">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
